snippet.title: Amber Heard CONFIRMS She's in Aquaman 2 - And Fighting for BIGGER ROLE?
snippet.description:
Amber Heard CONFIRMS She's in Aquaman 2 - And Fighting for BIGGER ROLE?

Amber Heard confirmed in an interview that she's back for Aquaman 2, and she's also giving her haters the finger.

But rumors persist concerning her role in the sequel. One says her role will reduced, but another says it could be bigger.

I discuss in this video, so check it out.
